ZH: 这件衣服是可逆的，可以两面穿。
EN: This clothing is reversible, you can wear it on both sides.

ZH: 这个函数是可逆的，可以通过逆向操作获取原来的输入。
EN: This function is reversible, you can obtain the original input through the inverse operation.

ZH: 这个化学反应是可逆的，可以逆向发生。
EN: This chemical reaction is reversible, it can occur in the opposite direction.

ZH: 这个门锁是可逆的，你可以从内部和外部解锁。
EN: This door lock is reversible, you can unlock it from both the inside and outside.

ZH: 这种瓷器是可逆转的，可以在破碎后修复。
EN: This type of porcelain is reversible, it can be repaired after being broken.

ZH: 这个开关是可逆的，可以切换灯的亮灭状态。
EN: This switch is reversible, it can toggle the on/off state of the light.

ZH: 宇宙的膨胀是可逆的，也可以收缩。
EN: The expansion of the universe is reversible, it can also contract.

ZH: 这是一个可逆反应，产物可以再次转化为反应物。
EN: This is a reversible reaction, the products can be converted back into the reactants.

ZH: 这个发型是可逆的，可以通过重新梳理变回原样。
EN: This hairstyle is reversible, it can be returned to its original form by combing it again.

ZH: 这个玩具是可逆组装的，可以拆解和重新组合。
EN: This toy is reversible in assembly, it can be disassembled and reassembled.

ZH: 这种短袖衬衫是可逆的，可以穿正面或背面。
EN: This type of short-sleeved shirt is reversible, you can wear it with the front or back facing out.

ZH: 这种翻译工作是可逆的，可以从中文翻译为英文，也可以从英文翻译为中文。
EN: This translation work is reversible, it can be translated from Chinese to English, or from English to Chinese.

ZH: 这个材料具有可逆的形变能力，可以在受力后恢复原状。
EN: This material has reversible deformation ability, it can return to its original shape after being subjected to force.

ZH: 这个开关是双向可逆的，可以从A端开关到B端，也可以从B端开关到A端。
EN: This switch is bidirectionally reversible, you can switch from terminal A to terminal B, or from terminal B to terminal A.

ZH: 这个电池充电器具有可逆的充放电功能，可以充电和放电电池。
EN: This battery charger has reversible charging and discharging functions, it can charge and discharge batteries.

ZH: 这条围巾是可逆的，正反两面都可以露出。
EN: This scarf is reversible, both sides can be exposed.

ZH: 这种材料的磁性是可逆的，可以通过外部磁场来改变。
EN: The magnetism of this material is reversible, it can be altered by an external magnetic field.

ZH: 这种风景画是可逆的，可以从一个角度看和从另一个角度看。
EN: This landscape painting is reversible, it can be viewed from one angle and from another angle.

ZH: 这个电动工具具有可逆的旋转方向，可以正转和反转。
EN: This power tool has reversible rotation direction, it can rotate forward and backward.

ZH: 这款手表是可逆配戴的，表盘可以翻转到内侧或外侧。
EN: This watch is reversible to wear, the dial can be flipped to the inside or outside.
